<p>The single most effective thing you can do to ensure a smooth installation is communicate clearly with every party involved — your fitter, your retailer, your trades and your worktop supplier. Keep a shared note of all dates, contact numbers and outstanding tasks. When everyone knows the plan, the plan is far more likely to run on time.</p>
